# Homepage Docs files

- Source of truth for the **Docs** tab: `public/docs/*.md`
- Nav order: `public/docs/manifest.json` (`pages[].id`, `title`, `file`)
- Renderer: `public/markdown.js` (headings, lists, tables, links, code) — keep docs within that subset
- Prefer short sections with stable `##` headings so future edits can target one section

When adding a new doc topic: create the `.md`, add it to `manifest.json`, and keep Overview links/wording consistent if needed.
